title: How to Have Patience
itunes:title: How to Have Patience
description:
Episode 146 - "Patience is bitter, but the fruit is sweet." It is hard to have patience when you look around and see all that you don't have and all that you are not. In this episode I talk about the keys to being patient and why having patience is one of the biggest key to being successful.
